data.description: Looking for country living in California? Well, here is your opportunity to own 6.1 acres (265,716 sq. ft.)! The home on the property was custom built in 1989 giving the family many years of enjoyment. The separate 1440sq. ft. garage/workshop is perfect for cars, trucks, equipment, etc. or to work on those special projects. With some TLC and vision, the potential for this property is endless.
